'''''Annealer''''' was an [[Acclamator-class transgalactic military assault ship/Legends|''Acclamator''-class assault ship]] of the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Republic Navy]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], ''Annealer'' was dispatched to [[Battle of Duro (Clone Wars)|defend]] [[Duro/Legends|Duro]]. There it was destroyed by [[General/Legends|General]] [[Grievous/Legends|Grievous]] during [[Operation Durge's Lance]].

